@Node "Changes" "mfkey - Changes"

mfkey 1.9
- GUI reworked
- List classes are now used by default
- Some minor changes and bug fixes

mfkey 1.8
- Added keyboard.device supported MMkeys (PLAY, STOP, PREV, NEXT)

mfkey 1.7
- Implemented a ParseIX() routine, because of
  commodities.library doesn't parse all keys
  correctly
- Some minor changes

mfkey 1.6
- Added Path
- Enabled WB start mode
- Some other changes

mfkey 1.5
- Many minor changes

mfkey 1.4
- Added Active menu item
- Fixed startup code

mfkey 1.3
- Added eat flag
- Cleaned some code
- Removed ARexx port
- Some minor changes

mfkey 1.2
- String fixed again
- Removed Iconify status, item and gadgets
- Other minor changes

mfkey 1.1
- Popasl button was not enabled/disabled: fixed
- Popasl requester was not opened with "me->pr_WindowPtr = (struct Window *)-1": fixed
- Strings fixed

mfey 1.0
- First release

@EndNode

